      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in poor condition \u2014 buyers should be fully aware of what they're getting before making a purchase. The exterior shows significant wear including multiple scratches, dents, and paint fading or chipping in several areas. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn or torn upholstery, staining, and general deterioration of trim and surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention \u2014 expect to budget for repairs. This listing is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the risks associated with a high-mileage, well-worn vehicle. What you see is what you get \u2014 no surprises hidden in the description.",
