      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and represents a solid, dependable used car at a fair price. The exterior shows some light signs of normal use \u2014 you may notice a few minor scratches or small paint scuffs here and there \u2014 but there are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns. The body panels align well and the overall appearance is presentable. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional; the upholstery has some wear consistent with regular use but no tears or major staining. All primary features and controls work as expected. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been maintained adequately \u2014 it's ready for daily driving without any immediate major repairs anticipated. This is a practical, honest buy for someone who wants a reliable vehicle without paying mint-condition prices.",
      "price": 34000.0,
